In fact, that ice on the top protects

00:05:21.648 --> 00:05:23.121
the water below from...

00:05:23.121 --> 00:05:25.744
You can imagine, the ice, it protects it

00:05:25.744 --> 00:05:27.727
from getting even further frozen

00:05:27.727 --> 00:05:30.135
and so you have animals

00:05:30.135 --> 00:05:34.060
able to just hang out.

